@endpoint PUT /subscriptions/{subscriptionId}/resourceGroups/{resourceGroupName}/providers/Microsoft.CustomerInsights/hubs/{hubName}/authorizationPolicies/{authorizationPolicyName}
@desc Creates an authorization policy or updates an existing authorization policy.
@required {authorizationPolicyName: any # The name of the policy., parameters: any # Parameters supplied to the CreateOrUpdate authorization policy operation.}
@returns(200) OK. Successfully update an existing authorization policy.
