@endpoint POST /subscriptions/{subscriptionId}/resourceGroups/{resourceGroupName}/providers/Microsoft.CustomerInsights/hubs/{hubName}/authorizationPolicies/{authorizationPolicyName}/regeneratePrimaryKey
@desc Regenerates the primary policy key of the specified authorization policy.
